Package tunes_part_2

Class FoothillTunesStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • tunes_part_2.FoothillTunesStore
  • public class FoothillTunesStore
extends java.lang.Object
    The FoothillTunesStore class creates and initalizes an object of LazySearchTree whose generic type is SongEntry. In the main method, creates an array of songs and adds them in to the FoothillTunesStore object of store. The method sort the songs based on their titles and experiments with removing the songs from the tree
